
1. How to run

   First install node.js: 

     yum install nodejs

   Install npm: 

     curl http://npmjs.org/install.sh | sh

   install packages: 

     npm install

   run: node server.js

2. How to test

   First start node.js:

     node server.js

   Install necessary gems(ensure ruby and bundler are installed): 

     bundle install

   run test: rake spec

3. Next to do
   (1) Add mongodb support
   (2) Support one simple scenario

